attributes.name: value-key
attributes.desc: key name of the input suggestion object for display

attributes.name: debounce
attributes.desc: debounce delay when typing, in milliseconds

attributes.name: placement
attributes.optionValue: top / top-start / top-end / bottom / bottom-start / bottom-end

attributes.name: fetch-suggestions
attributes.desc: a method to fetch input suggestions. When suggestions are ready, invoke `callback(data:[])` to return them to Autocomplete

attributes.name: popper-class
attributes.desc: custom class name for autocomplete's dropdown

attributes.name: trigger-on-focus
attributes.desc: whether show suggestions when input focus

attributes.name: select-when-unmatched
attributes.desc: whether to emit a `select` event on enter when there is no autocomplete match

attributes.name: hide-loading
attributes.desc: whether to hide the loading icon in remote search

attributes.name: popper-append-to-body
attributes.desc: whether to append the dropdown to body. If the positioning of the dropdown is wrong, you can try to set this prop to false

attributes.name: highlight-first-item
attributes.desc: whether to highlight first item in remote search suggestions by default

slots.desc: Custom content for input suggestions. The scope parameter is { item }

events.name: @select
events.desc: triggers when a suggestion is clicked

events.name: @change
events.desc: triggers when the icon inside Input value change
